      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "Sensei LMS < 4.5.2 - Arbitrary Private Message Sending via IDOR (CVE-2022-2080)\n\nThe plugin does not ensure that the sender of a private message is either the teacher or the original sender, allowing any authenticated user to send messages to arbitrary private conversation via a IDOR attack. Note: Attackers are not able to see responses/messages between the teacher and student",
